    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为您介绍《A列车 9 Version 5》</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运输模拟与城市建造的经典结合，现在以最终形态回归！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106160/extras/040ca23b314d1de56b649241f26b81a3.poster.avif?t=1769556898\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106160/extras/040ca23b314d1de56b649241f26b81a3.webm?t=1769556898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎，总裁先生</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一家新兴铁路公司的总裁，您的任务是打造一个无与伦比的运输网络，为繁荣的城市奠定基石。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先，在您认为有潜力的地区铺设铁路轨道。您是喜欢山区、海岸，还是湖畔？或者，您想重现并改造现实中的城市？游戏中提供了60个不同的场景，给您带来无穷的重玩乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106160/extras/0fd4b4ab259b3e6691d69282f78b11bd.avif?t=1769556898\" width=800 height=366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着城市围绕您的网络自然发展，您可以引导并塑造它，将其打造成属于您的理想乌托邦大都会。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过决定手动建造哪些建筑物，影响每个区域的发展。从500种不同建筑中进行选择！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用强大的地形编辑工具来平整障碍物、改道河流，或只是让城市更具起伏感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优化列车类型（包含97种列车）、最高速度以及运行时刻表，实现最大效率。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106160/extras/98d748769f4bd9540d11287351fcda2f.poster.avif?t=1769556898\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106160/extras/98d748769f4bd9540d11287351fcda2f.webm?t=1769556898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106160/extras/98d748769f4bd9540d11287351fcda2f.mp4?t=1769556898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>搭乘一程</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的城市正在逐步成形，这是放松的最佳时机！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坐在城市中繁忙行驶的列车驾驶座或乘客座，亲身体验您的铁路运输是多么舒适（或糟糕！）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坐在汽车的乘客座穿越城市，或坐在港口的船上，放松心情欣赏风景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者，从鸟瞰视角俯瞰整座城市，掌握全局！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106160/extras/dea0ff07e6a4a310ca150c040a51734f.poster.avif?t=1769556898\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106160/extras/dea0ff07e6a4a310ca150c040a51734f.webm?t=1769556898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106160/extras/dea0ff07e6a4a310ca150c040a51734f.mp4?t=1769556898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>有什么新功能？</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新增「调车场」、「列车验票闸口」和「列车连挂」功能，带来更逼真的游戏体验！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106160/extras/e279d30f52d95679f2e53943f72c143d.avif?t=1769556898\" width=800 height=366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
